{
  "text": "For the choice of hyperparameters, a set of possible values are first predefined, and the best hyperparameters are selected through 10-fold cross-validation, for all the competing methods. The RFS-LDA hyperparameters (as in Eq. (5)) are set with the same strategy as in [CITATION_1] ",
